properties.sourceTitle: BEITZEL RD & BOCHMANN RD, South Nanango
properties.description:
STAY INFORMED: South Nanango vegetation fire as at 2:00pm Wed 19 Aug
Bushfire warning level: ADVICE
Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) advises there is a bushfire in South Nanango.
You need to keep up to date and decide what actions you will take if the situation changes.
Currently as at 2:00pm Wednesday 19 August, there is a vegetation fire burning to the north of Beitzel Road and to the east of Bochmann Road. The fire is travelling in an north easterly direction. 
Multiple QFES fire crews are on scene working to control the blaze. 
People in the area will be affected by smoke, which will reduce visibility and air quality.
Call Triple Zero (000) immediately if you believe you or your property is under threat.
